EXPLANATION
BY THE LEGISLATIVE COUNCIL
OF
A N A C T
RELATING TO LABOR AND LABOR RELATIONS -- FIREFIGHTERS' ARBITRATION
***
1 This act would provide that all contractual provisions in a firefighters collective bargaining
2 agreement would continue until a successor agreement has been reached or an interest arbitration
3 award has been rendered.
4 This act would take effect upon passage.
